<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/735904-if-this-book-contained-a-parental-rating">If this book contained a parental rating, what would that be? What sort of content is in this book on a scale from 1-10?
Violence:
Language:
Sex:
Drugs:
That sort of thing...I wish that there was some forum that contained parental notes on books. I can&#39;t find Clive Barker&#39;s books on any of the existing ones. Any help or info would be awesome. Thanks everyone!</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_735904'><a id="like_count_community_question_735904" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/735904?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">1 like</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F52640.Weaveworld">like</a></span>

