    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_64399473" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/64399473" />
    <a title="Dreadlocksmile" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/2075479-dreadlocksmile"><img alt="Dreadlocksmile" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1235682023p2/2075479.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/64399473?book_show_action=true">Jul 21, 2009</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Dreadlocksmile" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Dreadlocksmile" href="/user/show/2075479-dreadlocksmile">Dreadlocksmile</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer64399473" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7758879882808365797">Barker lets loose his imagination as he takes you on an unforgettable trip to fantastic and incredible worlds of pure fantasy. His writing style engrosses the reader deep within the pages, immersing you into a dark and wonderful land of the unbelievable. He takes you on a trip of the magical and macabre and celebrates the potential of the human imagination.<br/><br/>The novel will grip you from the start and keep you desperate to keep reading. It is a book of dark fantasy that leaves you breathless after </span>
  <span id="freeText7758879882808365797" style="display:none">Barker lets loose his imagination as he takes you on an unforgettable trip to fantastic and incredible worlds of pure fantasy. His writing style engrosses the reader deep within the pages, immersing you into a dark and wonderful land of the unbelievable. He takes you on a trip of the magical and macabre and celebrates the potential of the human imagination.<br /><br />The novel will grip you from the start and keep you desperate to keep reading. It is a book of dark fantasy that leaves you breathless after each page. First published back in 1987, the novel has remained one of the most talked about of Barker's books to date.<br /><br />With so many of Barker's novels, you can't help but wonder at the symbolism within the stories. The characters often reflect and resemble his ideas and views on his life and the society around him. This brings in a whole new level to the book, where one starts to interpret the messages and moral dilemmas within the pages.<br /><br />Weaveworld will leave your head spinning with thoughts and feelings once you finally put the book down, finished. It will teleport you slowly back to reality with a memory of the fantastic and magical. Nothing comes close to the escape of a novel of such talent and imagination. A book to love forever.</span>
  <a data-text-id="7758879882808365797" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

